<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nova Autoland Promotional Banner Demo</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Nova Autoland Promotional Banner Demo</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-200 relative">
        <img 
          src="https://imagescdn.dealercarsearch.com/Media/23726/22303830/638811988519848181.jpg" 
          alt="2004 Toyota RAV4"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute top-2 right-2 bg-white py-1 px-2 rounded text-sm font-bold">
          $7,495
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-4">
        <!-- Nova Autoland Promotion Banner -->
        <div class="mb-3">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0a2158] text-white p-3 rounded">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-[60px] bg-[#ff6c00] opacity-20"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">4-Month Warranty!</div>
              <div class="text-sm">Free Oil Change • Free Brake Pads • Free Battery</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="absolute right-3 bottom-3">
              <div class="bg-[#ff6c00] text-white text-xs font-bold py-1 px-3 rounded-full">
                LIMITED TIME OFFER
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 truncate">2004 Toyota RAV4</h3>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">$7,495</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center text-neutral-600 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-2 text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22a10 10 0 1 0 0-20 10 10 0 0 0 0 20Z"></path>
              <path d="M16.8 13a4 4 0 1 1-8 0"></path>
              <path d="M12 22V20"></path>
              <path d="M12 4v4"></path>
              <path d="M12 8v4h4"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>86,921 miles</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center text-neutral-600 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-2 text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M3 21h18"></path>
              <path d="M19 21v-4"></path>
              <path d="M19 17a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"></path>
              <path d="M11 17v-6"></path>
              <path d="M7 17v-6"></path>
              <path d="M13 7V3h8v4"></path>
              <path d="M13 7h8"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Nova Autoland</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center text-neutral-600 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 mr-2 text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span>Chantilly, VA</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Implementation Details:</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">This is a demonstration of how the Nova Autoland promotional banner appears on vehicle cards from Nova Autoland dealership. The actual implementation includes:</p>
      
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Dynamic detection of Nova Autoland vehicles in the <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">SafeVehicleCard</code> and <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">VehicleCard</code> components</li>
        <li>Responsive design that works on both mobile and desktop layouts</li>
        <li>Eye-catching navy blue background with orange accents</li>
        <li>Clear presentation of the warranty and free services</li>
        <li>Attention-grabbing "LIMITED TIME OFFER" badge</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>The banner only appears for vehicles from Nova Autoland dealership. All other dealership vehicles will not show this promotional banner.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>